"staticPWContent" : "Create bitcoin private and public key pairs. You may even disconnect your internet connection and still generate new bitcoin addresses offline. Before using a bitcoin address to store your bitcoin, it is MANDATORY that you take the print out of the key pair generated or else you will never be able to spend the bitcoin sent to that address (hence called paper wallet). To make your work even easier, whenever you want to withdraw Unocoin wallet bitcoin to the bitcoin address in your safe/paper wallet, you will be provided an option to add that bitcoin address to your address book after you hit the PRINT button. You may even assign a nickname to that bitcoin address so that you may identify it easily in future. When you add the bitcoin address to your address book, only the bitcoin address gets passed on to our server and not the private key. "staticPWContent" : "बिटकॉइन प्राइवेट और पब्लिक कुंजी पेयर्स(key pairs) बनाएं। आप अपने इंटरनेट कनेक्शन को डिस्कनेक्ट भी कर सकते हैं और फिर भी ऑफ़लाइन नए बिटकॉइन पते उत्पन्न कर सकते हैं। उत्पन्न बिटकॉइन कुंजी जोड़े हमारे सर्वर द्वारा ज्ञात नहीं होंगे। अपने बिटकॉइन को स्टोर करने के लिए बिटकॉइन एड्रेस का उपयोग करने से पहले, यह अनिवार्य है कि आप प्रिंट की गई महत्वपूर्ण कुंजी जोड़ी का प्रिंट आउट लेते हैं वरना आप उस पते पर भेजे गए बिटकॉइन को खर्च नहीं कर पाएंगे (इसलिए पेपर वॉलेट कहा जाता है)। अपने काम को और भी आसान बनाने के लिए, जब भी आप अपने सुरक्षित / पेपर वॉलेट में बिटकॉइन पते पर Unocoin वॉलेट बिटकॉइन को वापस लेना चाहते हैं, तो आपको प्रिंट बटन हिट करने के बाद उस बिटकॉइन पते को अपनी एड्रेस बुक में जोड़ने का विकल्प प्रदान किया जाएगा। आप उस बिटकॉइन पते पर एक उपनाम भी निर्दिष्ट कर सकते हैं ताकि आप इसे भविष्य में आसानी से पहचान सकें। जब आप बिटकॉइन एड्रेस को अपनी एड्रेस बुक में जोड़ते हैं, तो हमारे सर्वर पर केवल बिटकॉइन एड्रेस ही होता है, न कि प्राइवेट कुंजी(key)। आप अपने अन्य बिटकॉइन पते और अपने मित्र के बिटकॉइन पते को भी एड्रेस बुक में जोड़ सकते हैं। एड्रेस बुक तब सहायक होती है जब आपको बाद में उन पते पर बिटकॉइन भेजने की आवश्यकता होती है।"

playstore_details.description:
Unocoin

About Unocoin
Unocoin is India’s leading Crypto asset and Blockchain Company with over a million customers.
We make it easy to buy, sell, store, use & accept crypto assets (BTC, ETH, XRP, LTC, BCH, BTG...) securely in India. We have a few achievements under our belt:

Raised 5 million + USD in funding from top investors like Blume Ventures, ah! Ventures, Mumbai Angels, Boost VC, Digital Currency Group, FundersClub, Future perfect Ventures, Huiyin Blockchain Ventures, Draper Associates.
Featured among the Top 20 out of 350 companies in the The Fintech 20: India list.
Unocoin is a member of NASSCOM.
Picked amongst the Top 20 technology startups for Tech30 2017 by YourStory India.

Unocoin has one mission – Bringing Bitcoin to Billions.

Merger of Unocoin and Unodax: 
Unocoin is the next generation of Unodax, a platform specifically designed for individual crypto traders. If you’re an existing Unodax customer, you will be able to go to unocoin.com/exchange today and will notice a number of new features, including:

All transactions and balances from Unodax will automatically appear in Unocoin Exchange
A completely redesigned platform that will make the trading experience easier and more intuitive
‘My Wallets’ for a new consolidated portfolio which shows an overview of your account order and balances
Simplified deposit and withdrawal processes
Instead of only Bitcoin and USDT, wallet page now brings 30 different coins

On both Unodax and Unocoin, you will have direct access to Unocoin, the single liquidity pool shared by all Unocoin products. On logging into the Unocoin, you will be able to see your existing Unodax balance and trade history and enjoy the same trading fees, APIs and security features that today’s platform provides.

Highlights:
Buy/Sell Bitcoin/Ether/USDT instantly
Low transaction fees
Consolidated wallet for crypto-holdings
Supports multiple crypto assets
Transact (Send/Request) in crypto assets
Accept/Request crypto assets
Earn free Bitcoin by referring Unocoin to your friends
Deposit/Withdraw INR
Mobile/DTH Recharge with Bitcoin
New features include: Lending, Earn Interest, Crypto Basket, SBP, Altcoin Conversion, Autosell, NETKI, Paper wallet.
Live Price Tracker Widget
Latest updates/news from Unocoin

Crypto Basket:
Go a step further in placing an order with new weighted basket orders. Presenting the Crypto Basket on Unocoin app - To read more about the Crypto Basket, click here.

Bitcoin/Ether SBP subscription
Hedge against the market volatility using Unocoin SBP (Systematic Buy Plan) module to automate bitcoin buying with a fixed amount and frequency.

Lending
Verified users can avail loans in USDT and INR in a straightforward procedure through a secured dashboard. Place a loan order against a collateral amount and manage your investments, fund expenses and plan tax routines.

Earn Interest
Opt for a fixed deposit of USDT (stable coin) and receive monthly payments as interest until the amount matures.

Unocoin blog for latest updates
Keep abreast of latest trends in crypto, Bitcoin & Blockchain developments and merchant partnerships for Bitcoin payments at https://blog.unocoin.com and get involved in hot discussions in the Crypto asset space. For important alerts, keep an eye on https://news.unocoin.com

Youtube channel for help
Head on to our YouTube Channel (https://m.youtube.com/channel/UCxTztdOn_HjYhMGiT8su6Bg) for engaging step-by-step tutorials on availing services from https://unocoin.com along with new developments in the Bitcoin space.

Support details of Unocoin
For further support please go to https://www.unodax.com/contactus
Mail: support@unocoin.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Unocoin
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Unocoin

Support Service
Telegram: http://t.me/Unocoin_Group
Toll-free number: +91 7788978910 (9:30 – 6:30, Mon-Sat).

Conditions Apply
For detailed terms & conditions, please refer: https://www.unocoin.com/post/98
